== 賽車中的超車 ==
賽車中的超車可以在轉彎或直路的位置發生。轉彎超車可以憑藉比對手遲剎車，再擋著對手的行車線而達成。直路超車則需要與對手的車尾緊貼，藉著前車的{{le|滑流|Slipstream}}為自己製造有利條件<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://link.springer.com/article/10.1007/BF03247078 |title=Fiumara, F. Analysis of an overtaking manoeuvre. ATZ Autotechnol 8, 64–68 (2008) |access-date=2021-02-01 |archive-date=2017-04-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170418062711/http://link.springer.com/article/10.1007/BF03247078 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.trackdays.co.uk/news/what-is-a-slipstream/|title=The science of slipstreaming - what is it, and how does it work?|publisher=TrackDays|access-date=2021-02-01|archive-date=2021-02-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210204193755/https://www.trackdays.co.uk/news/what-is-a-slipstream/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

